    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8 text-left">
      <h2>AI agent memory products compared</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">The market has fragmented into four territories. Only one quadrant — engine-agnostic + agent-centric — is unoccupied:</p>

